{"meta":{"title":"Hexo","subtitle":"","description":"","author":"John Doe","url":"http://yoursite.com","root":"/index.html/"},"pages":[],"posts":[{"title":"ocaml_ch_01","slug":"ocaml-ch-01","date":"2020-11-10T12:21:31.000Z","updated":"2020-11-11T16:10:00.465Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/11/10/ocaml-ch-01/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/11/10/ocaml-ch-01/","excerpt":"","text":"OCaml Code Snippets局部定义12let x = 1 in let y = x + x in let z = y + y in x + y + z;;- : int = 7 in 语法形式化语义 (let x = 1 in x + x) = (x + x)[x := 1] = 1+1 = 2 普通递归形式斐波那契数列12345678let rec fib x = if x &lt; 0 then 0 else if x = 1 || x = 2 then 1 else fib(x - 1) + fib(x-2);;for i = 1 to 20 do printf \"fib[%d] = %d\\n\" i (fib i)done;; 尾递归形式斐波那契数列此时相当于转换成了循环形式，loop 0 -&gt;loop 1 -&gt; loop … -&gt; loop n 12345678910let fib_tail n = let rec loop i a b = if i &gt; n then 0 else if i = n then a else loop (i+1)(b)(a+b) in loop 0 0 1;;for i = -2 to 20 do printf \"fib_tail[%d] = %d\\n\" i (fib_tail i)done;;","categories":[{"name":"Coding","slug":"Coding","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/Coding/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Code Ocaml","slug":"Code-Ocaml","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/Code-Ocaml/"}]},{"title":"LLVM插桩","slug":"LLVM插桩","date":"2020-11-08T10:46:21.000Z","updated":"2020-11-10T12:46:25.460Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/11/08/LLVM插桩/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/11/08/LLVM%E6%8F%92%E6%A1%A9/","excerpt":"","text":"LLVM Pass DevelopmentReference https://llvm.org/devmtg/2019-10/slides/Warzynski-WritingAnLLVMPass.pdf","categories":[{"name":"Coding","slug":"Coding","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/Coding/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Code LLVM C++","slug":"Code-LLVM-C","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/Code-LLVM-C/"}]},{"title":"HelloWorld","slug":"HelloWorld","date":"2020-11-07T16:43:29.000Z","updated":"2020-11-10T12:47:11.154Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/11/08/HelloWorld/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/11/08/HelloWorld/","exc